*
*===dpoli==============================================================*
*
CDECK  ID>, DT_DPOLI
      SUBROUTINE DT_DPOLI(CS,SI)

      IMPLICIT DOUBLE PRECISION (A-H,O-Z)
      SAVE

      U  = DT_RNDM(CS)
      CS = DT_RNDM(U)
      IF (U.LT.0.5D0) CS=-CS
      SI = SQRT(1.0D0-CS*CS+1.0D-10)

      RETURN
      END


 
 

