     &        LDSCGM, LNDSLD, LMNJPR, LBRPEN, LNWBRP, LIFKEY, LOLDSM,
     &        LNAIPR, LGUSPR, LFLKCO, LLVMOD, LHVEVP, LHVECN, LHVCAL,
     &        LHVRAL, LHVSGF, LTMCRR, LBZZCR, LQCSKP, LPEXLV, LEEXLV,
